A bustling Indian tech office in the late 2000s rendered in warm Studio Ghibli animation style, featuring a circular arrangement of wooden chairs around a low table where diverse professionals in business casual attire lean forward in animated discussion, papers and laptops scattered between them. Through large windows, the Chennai skyline glows golden with sunset light, dotted with construction cranes suggesting rapid urban growth. In the foreground, empty chairs multiply and stretch toward the horizon, symbolizing exponential expansion. Potted jasmine plants and brass lamps add local character. The mood is energetic yet slightly overwhelming, with swirling warm colors of saffron, teal, and cream conveying both opportunity and chaos.
